title: Logic Music?
body:
Dude. idk what this login music is, but it is awesome. Some like pop/techno wordless vocals, and it shouldn't be awesome, but it's freakin' awesome.

Who/what is that?

replies.body: It's hard to say, I'd call it trance-hype!  :P  Ask this over at our[ sound boards](http://boards.na.leagueoflegends.com/en/c/story-art) to discuss it with the community!
